---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy | ToolGrid" description="Information about how ToolGrid uses cookies.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Cookie Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">ToolGrid respects your privacy and utilizes a minimal cookie footprint.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What are cookies?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Cookies are small pieces of text sent to your web browser by a website you visit. They help that website remember information about your visit.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">How we use them</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">Because our tools operate purely in the browser without accounts, we do not use tracking or advertising cookies. Any local storage or session storage used is strictly necessary to maintain the functional state of the tools while you use them.</p>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
